# 1. Domain Redirect (Permanent - 301!)
# Redirects all traffic from the old Netlify subdomain to the new custom domain, preserving the path.
https://reflexinteractive.netlify.app/* https://www.reflexinteractive.com/:splat 301!

---

# 2. Clean URLs (Explicit Rewrites - 200)
# Rewrites a clean public path to an actual file location for content pages.
/games          /src/pages/games.html       200
/newswire       /src/pages/newswire.html    200
/contact        /src/pages/contact.html     200
/about          /src/pages/about.html       200

---

# 3. Dynamic Content Handler (Splat Rewrites - 200)
# Handles all specific game detail paths and serves the single template file.
/game-details/* /src/pages/game-details.html   200

---

# 4. Catch-All Fallback (Root Index Rewrite - 200)
# If a path doesn't match a rule above or an existing file, it falls back to the root 'index.html'.
# This is crucial for Single Page Application (SPA) routing.
/* /index.html 200